  <brief_title>Patient Convenience Study (RE-SONANCE)</brief_title>
  <official_title>Non-interventional Study Describing PatientsÂ´ Perception on Anticoagulant Treatment and Treatment Convenience When Treated With Pradaxa or Vitamine K Antagonist for Stroke Prevention in Non-Valvular Atrial Fibrillation</official_title>
